                A 25% growth target is most plausible if a material share of incremental revenue comes from high-growth, non-commoditised areas:
              </p>
            </div>
          </Reveal>
          
          <div className="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mt-12">
